 '#'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'Reset' ‚ćĚ Clean out any previous GUI work

 'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'New' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
 'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'New' 'Selector'
 'f.s.p1'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s.p1'‚äĘ'New' 'Page'('caption' 'One')
 'f.s.p2'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s.p2'‚äĘ'New' 'Page'('caption' 'Two')

 ext‚Üź'f.s'‚ąÜWI'size' ‚ćĚ Get the size of the Selector
 'f.s.p1'‚ąÜWI Pass ext‚äĘ'extent' ‚ćĚ And make sure the Page takes up the whole thing

 'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'p1' 'p2'‚äĘ'pages'
 'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 1‚äĘ'value'

 'f.s.p1'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'onValidate' 'PVal‚Üź2 2‚äÉ‚ąÜWARG'
